@boredape8677 The SetApprovalForAll func takes 2 parameters: "Operator" & "Approved". "Operator" is to whom you want to grant permission, it's the OS contract for your case. "Approved" is the status to set, "true" means you want to approve, "false" or nothing means you want to revoke.
@boredape8677 "Set Approval for All" function is used to Set (true) and Revoke (false) the approval
